.TH PRODBOX_docs 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-docs \- Generated-documentation maintenance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox docs
.SH DESCRIPTION
Check or regenerate marker-delimited documentation sections.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBcheck\fR
Check generated docs for drift
.TP
\fBgenerate\fR
Regenerate generated docs
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox docs check\fR
Check generated documentation sections for drift.
